WEBVTT

00:03:29.301 --> 00:03:33.478
Štaviše, vitezovi u „Ekskaliburu“
nose svoj oklop svuda.

00:03:33.502 --> 00:03:37.025
Sve vreme - nose ga na večeri,
nose ga u krevetu.

00:03:37.049 --> 00:03:38.100
(Smeh)

00:03:38.124 --> 00:03:39.994
Bio sam u fazonu: „Zar mi čitaju misli?

00:03:40.018 --> 00:03:42.486
Ja hoću stalno da nosim oklop!“

00:03:42.510 --> 00:03:43.525
(Smeh)

00:03:43.549 --> 00:03:45.748
Tako sam se vratio
svom omiljenom materijalu,

00:03:45.772 --> 00:03:47.321
prelaznoj drogi za izradu,

00:03:47.345 --> 00:03:48.765
rebrastom kartonu,

00:03:48.789 --> 00:03:51.651
i napravio sam oklop za sebe,

00:03:51.675 --> 00:03:55.120
pun štitnika za vrat, i belog konja.

00:03:55.144 --> 00:03:56.410
Sad kad sam ga precenio,

00:03:56.434 --> 00:03:58.460
evo slike oklopa koji sam napravio.

00:03:58.484 --> 00:03:59.825
(Smeh)

00:03:59.849 --> 00:04:02.299
(Aplauz)